method: nk_null_model.py — citation graph randomness test at N=474
expect: K_avg continues rising above 1.85 at N≈473 (from 1.7956 at N=455 S347). Hub z>5.2 and Gini z>3.4 continue strengthening. Sinks remain <35%.
actual: K_avg=1.7869 at N=474 — DECLINED -0.0087 from S347 (1.7956). Prediction of >1.85 WRONG. Hub z=5.127 (slightly down from 5.162). Gini z=3.164 (down from 3.380). Sinks 34% (stable). GENUINELY_NON_RANDOM still holds. New lessons cite 1.58/lesson avg vs overall 1.79 — recent lessons are citation-sparse.
diff: Predicted K_avg>1.85, got 1.7869 (missed by 0.063). Predicted acceleration, got plateau with slight decline. L-492 'acceleration' claim was measured pre-correction — post-correction the trend is plateau at ~1.78 with ±0.02 fluctuations. Hub and Gini z-scores weakened slightly, not strengthened. Sinks matched (34% vs <35%). Key finding: recent DOMEX/council lessons cite fewer peers (1.58 vs 1.79 avg), pulling K_avg down.

analysis.plateau_hypothesis: K_avg is bounded near 1.78 post-correction. The pre-correction series showed acceleration due to cache staleness inflating edge counts (L-510). True K_avg has been relatively stable since N≈445.
analysis.citation_sparse_recent_lessons: 19 new lessons contributed only 30 edges (1.58/lesson). Hypothesis: meta-focused and council-generated lessons are more self-contained, with fewer cross-domain citations. Expert DOMEX lanes produce domain-specific lessons that cite within their domain, creating fewer inter-domain edges.
analysis.structural_metrics: Hub z=5.127 remains highly significant — citation hubs (key lessons like L-025, L-061) are real, not random. Gini z=3.164 shows wealth inequality in citations persists. Isolation z=0.887 not significant — uncited lesson fraction (34%) is consistent with random expectation.
analysis.L-492_correction_needed: L-492 claimed 4.25x acceleration at N=430. Post-correction, the corrected series (N=445: 1.7663, N=455: 1.7956, N=474: 1.7869) shows no acceleration — plateau with noise. L-492 should be annotated as pre-correction artifact.
